===Etymology 1===
{{ja-kanjitab|みさお|y=k}}
Compound of {{ja-com|sort=みさお|御|み-|pos1=honorific prefix often emphasizing beauty|青|あお|t2=[[blue]], [[green]]}}, in the sense of the quality of an unchanging beautiful green in the face of anything, similar to an evergreen tree. The medial ''-s-'' may represent {{w|epenthesis}} between two vowels, or it may be cognate with {{cog|ko|-}} interfix {{m|ko|-ㅅ-|tr=-s-}} used to mark possession, much like {{noncog|de|-s-}}.  See also {{ja-r|小%雨|こ%さめ|[[drizzle]]}}, {{ja-r|霧%雨|きり%さめ|drizzle}}, {{ja-r|春%雨|はる%さめ|[[spring]] [[rain]]}}, and {{ja-r|稲|しね|[[rice]]}}.

